{"tid":1173372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【孕照留念】讚52歲懷孕妻陳麗麗 黃澤鋒：大肚得嚟好有型","createTime":"2019-05-27T05:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T01:09:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7668bf436a858a270df79d85ebd906b53978224e","tid":1173372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"黃澤鋒年初宣佈52歲老婆陳麗麗懷孕，囡囡乳名叫「小黃妃」，老婆早前受妊娠濕疹影響，全身又痕又痛，幸好有老公黃澤鋒悉心照顧（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TbFkEL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TbFkEL&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=e7e3533a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TbFkEL</a> ），目前已痊癒，黃澤鋒亦小心照顧懷孕愛妻的日常起居飲食，二人坦言有意再追B。<br />\n他們早前拍攝懷孕照留念，黃澤鋒接受《蘋果》訪問時說：「今次影呢輯相係我第一次同太太叫『三個人』一齊影相。」黃澤鋒指他們結婚時沒影婚照，當時只以簡單衣着去影相，陳麗麗續道：「我哋係諗住有B嘅時候就會將件事鋪大啲，希望留嚟紀念，今次有個好朋友提議幫我哋影輯相，我哋都好開心呀！拍手掌話好，我哋去影喇！」<br />\n黃澤鋒讚這輯相影得太太又靚又有型，他賣口乖說：「大肚得嚟都好有型！真係影得好靚、好開心。」陳麗麗笑指：「大家都OK，今次係一個好好嘅留念，而家陀B約32周，預產期喺7月，重咗好多，80公斤。」黃澤鋒解釋：「佢就80公斤，B女好似重咗，但佢個肚好大個。」陳麗麗稱B女目前3磅幾：「OK嘅！都健健康康，不過肚大，個人累贅啲，行路辛苦啲，其他都so far so good！」黃澤鋒自言越來越緊張，因為即將步入「終點」，迎接愛女出世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190527/large/1558926581_d894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558926581_d894.jpg&h=1b99f016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190527/large/1558926785_b950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558926785_b950.jpg&h=16af7782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190527/large/1558926785_45d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558926785_45d2.jpg&h=bb94d223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190527/large/1558926785_7aba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558926785_7aba.jpg&h=3a3a1fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190527/large/1558926788_182c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558926788_182c.jpg&h=e0d55e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190527/large/1558926788_f68a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558926788_f68a.jpg&h=78922bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190527/large/1558926789_78dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190527%2Flarge%2F1558926789_78dd.jpg&h=de7b7c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190527/59645459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F59645459&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=46a59760\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F59645459&h=48f34a5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190527/59645459</a>"},{"pid":"aee49233027878969d3ee4e03507fcba75a7244b","tid":1173372,"uid":20302,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"人地會問 呢個你個孫？"},{"pid":"f010c5769ad7be250696a8d9db2d97640e6e0ce8","tid":1173372,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"上中學 父母就退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\